::Ramulus::

Ramulus frowns. A bot who had kidnapped two bots, refusing to give even one 
up, and now wanted to meet him one on one, didn't sound very trustworthy.

"Actually, if we attacked you on your way, you'd execute Striker," Ramulus 
points out, "And if you don't give us Spears, its not a good step toward us 
meeting. Like this we'll at least have half of our kidnapped troups, a sort 
of gain even if I meet you and you don't give me Striker. If you take Spears 
back, how do I know you'll give her up later?"
